          This is content color swatch "B" and a preview of a
          = succeed "." do
            %a.ui-link{:href => "#"} link
        %a{"data-inline" => "true", "data-role" => "button", :href => "#"} Button
      %h2 Swatch C
      %div{"data-role" => "header", "data-theme" => "c"}
